        <h2>Member Information Form</h2>
        <p>All members are required to complete a member information form prior to the pool opening on May 24. <i><u>Starting Opening Day, your family will not be 
        given access to the pool until the membership form is submitted.</u></i></p>
        <p>Please fill out the 2026 Membership Information Form and email it to <a href="mailto:beechwoodswimclubky@gmail.com">beechwoodswimclubky@gmail.com</a>. The form can be found by clicking <a href="https://beechwoodswimclub.us18.list-manage.com/track/click?u=d2234782ae340940dd72dad5c&id=cc4eff24e8&e=c702d2f988">here</a>.</p>
      </div>    
