    </section>

    <section class="[ post-list ] [ pad-top-700 pad-bottom-300 ]">
      <div class="[ inner-wrapper ] [ sf-flow ]">
        <h2 style="text-decoration: underline;">A few reminders:</h2>
        <h2>Beechwood Barracudas Swim and Dive Team</h2>
        <p>Registration for the Beechwood Barracudas Swim and Dive Team is still open!</p>
        <p>Joining the Barracudas is more than just participating in a sport; it's about making lifelong friends, boosting confidence, and creating lasting summer memories. Our team competes in the Northern Kentucky Swim League (NKSL), providing a friendly, yet competitive environment for all skill levels.</p>
        <p>For more information and to register, visit the team online via Team Unify (<a href="https://www.gomotionapp.com/team/recnkbscky/page/home">https://www.gomotionapp.com/team/recnkbscky/page/home</a>). Additional information about the season can be found on the Team Unify site too. Check it out!</p>
        <p>Important dates for the Beechwood Barracudas Swim and Dive Team:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Information Night: Wednesday, May 28th at 7pm at the Lower Deck Shelter. Meet the coaches, learn about the season, and get all your questions answered. Athletes are welcome too!</li>
          <li>Practices Begin: Monday, June 2nd for the Swim/Dive Team; Tuesday, June 3rd for Little Cudas</li>
        </ul>
      </div>    

      <div class="[ inner-wrapper ] [ sf-flow ]">
        <h2>Membership Tags</h2>
        <p>Besides getting the pool ready we are working hard to get our new cards/tags ready! These will be able to be put on your keychain. You will receive your new tags at your first visit to the Swim Club. You will need your tags to scan in every time you visit.  We will no longer allow the front desk staff to look members up for entry.  This delays other members being able to enter in a timely fashion. To ensure quick entry into the Swim Club please have your tag ready or a picture of it to scan into the computer. If a look up is required, the manager will be called to the front office to help you.</p>
        <p>Replacement tags will be $5 per tag.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="[ inner-wrapper ] [ sf-flow ]">
